query:
select l_orderkey, l_suppkey, l_quantity, l_extendedprice,  l_discount, l_tax, l_returnflag, l_linestatus, l_shipdate, l_commitdate, l_receiptdate, l_shipmode
from lineitem
where l_returnflag = 'R'
